collection.name: Angry Ape Army Evolution Collection
collection.description:
The Angry Ape Army have modified their own kind to create "Evolved Apes." They were to be used as weapons against the humans but quickly the experiments went out of control.

 These lab grown apes are now roaming the metaverse destroying and taking control of all that come in it's path. Take control of an "Evolved Ape" and have superior battle advantage or spawn a Goliath x Golem by combining 4 evo apes. 

Become an OG ape holder and gain access to *free mints and more 

**Join the Revolution!!!**

[Angry Ape Army](https://opensea.io/collection/angry-ape-army)

[AAA Evolution Collection](https://opensea.io/collection/angry-ape-army-evolution-collection)
